{"tid":442199,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鄰國76歲廢老向飛機引擎投幣祈福 累全機乘客及機組人員滯留一天","createTime":"2017-10-20T11:31:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-20T12:53:57.000Z","uid":136994,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"aa65e952405ce7d3c1760a5aa228e70450942e1c","tid":442199,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T11:31:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20171020/20189069\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Finternational%2Fart%2F20171020%2F20189069&d=BpxmFN32749DdikvfqNz2pUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=38620bb5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Finternational%2Fart%2F20171020%2F20189069&h=bce70c11\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20171020/20189069</a><br />\n<br />\n內地又有旅客把飛機引擎當作許願池，祥鵬航空一名女乘客登上內陸機時，向飛機引擎投擲硬幣，認為可以保平安，事後被機場職員發現。為確保飛行安全，航空公司取消航班，重新檢查客機，全機乘客及機組人員滯留一天。公安機關介入調查，並控制涉事乘客。<br />\n<br />\n據祥鵬航空官方微博，編號8L9960航班，原定前天下午3時40分從安徽安慶前往雲南昆明。76歲姓方女乘客當天首次搭飛機，她認為丟硬幣可以祈求平安，於是登機時向飛機引擎投擲硬幣，剛好有機場職員看見，立即制止。隨後，機務人員在引擎附近位置的地上找到一枚硬幣。<br />\n<br />\n為確保飛行安全，祥鵬航空取消航班，重新檢查引擎。由於檢查需時，祥鵬航空安排乘客翌日早上10時搭機離開安慶，全機乘客被迫滯留一天，航空公司為受影響旅客提供酒店住宿及膳食。<br />\n<br />\n目前，公安機關已介入調查，並控制涉事乘客，祥鵬航空表示事件對飛行安全造成不良影響，將根據公安部門調查結果，保留追究當事人法律責任的權利。<br />\n其實今年6月27日曾發生乘客向飛機引擎「掟銀仔」，南方航空一班由上海浦東飛往廣州的航班，一名老婦聲稱為了祈福，在登機樓梯上向飛機引擎狂撒硬幣，令飛機引擎內充滿異物，必須重新檢查，導致航班延誤5個多小時。"},{"pid":"d5369008fbe63aba8d9f2fc58d31f1976c8f0ae7","tid":442199,"uid":40812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T11:33:59.000Z","msg":"唔係第一單？"},{"pid":"9043c2b08a17d30a06343ea37bbd76987fff6f01","tid":442199,"uid":20448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T11:51:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 痴線強國啊婆"},{"pid":"fe55a6646a1801662339f5160b5862357b96f8ea","tid":442199,"uid":70786,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T11:54:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係第一單？</blockquote><br />\n仲以為回帶撚<br />\n睇下個日期<br />\n支那畜真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15b026f9124d9eb9d73964665bdd3be7f50e1832","tid":442199,"uid":134220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T11:54:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係第一單？</blockquote><br />\n第一單係南方航空"},{"pid":"380e2ab7ae3ee076959dda396b0b3588d73b624f","tid":442199,"uid":134220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T11:55:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係第一單？</blockquote><br />\n呢間係海航個仔"},{"pid":"1c9c094c334519b5178cb1bf9f65c79c12b4f94c","tid":442199,"uid":293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T11:59:51.000Z","msg":"又一單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80dcad7da343596f85f8aebbe36d7d6e6b628814","tid":442199,"uid":121476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T12:02:40.000Z","msg":"生番就係生番"},{"pid":"86cda22801ef8fcabad4d5e053888acf84836768","tid":442199,"uid":31254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T12:06:50.000Z","msg":"投幣保你全機落地獄<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95a404c5e725d68930ccb00804355a2dee2592cc","tid":442199,"uid":110832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T12:10:47.000Z","msg":"民智未開嘅國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"784ccc2d9c825c0fc01d7774470f737863a19f41","tid":442199,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T12:19:17.000Z","msg":"狂撒硬幣果單都係導致航班延誤5個多小時，但係76歲個廢老就要停一日 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16df0ac298c77e37417ece92fd5367895ebd07d6","tid":442199,"uid":73695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T12:22:29.000Z","msg":"拋銀仔冇用，成個人衝去引擎先夠神心<img src=\"/asset